      <h1 class='title'>Canteen Facilities</h1>
    </div>
    <div class='commons-written-statements-sitting' id='content'>
      
      <cite class='section'>HC Deb 16 September 2004 vol 424 c1731WS</cite>
      <a class='permalink column-permalink' id='column_1731ws' title='Col. 1731WS &mdash; HC Deb 16 September 2004 vol 424 c1731WS' name='column_1731ws' href='#column_1731ws' rel='bookmark'>1731WS</a>
      <div class='hentry member_contribution'>
        <a name='S6CV0424P2_20040916_CWS2_475'>  </a>
        <blockquote cite='http://hansard.millbanksystems.com/people/mr-david-willetts' class='contribution_text entry-content'>
          <a class='speech-permalink permalink' href='#S6CV0424P2_20040916_CWS2_475' title='Link to this speech by Mr David Willetts' rel='bookmark'>&sect;</a>
          <cite class='member author entry-title'><a href="/people/mr-david-willetts" title="Mr David Willetts">Mr. Willetts</a></cite>
          <p class="first-para">To ask the Secretary of State for Work and Pensions what the cost of running his Department's canteen facilities was in<span class="italic">(a)</span>1996&#x2013;97 and <span class="italic">(b)</span> the latest year for which figures are available.[185529]</p>
        </blockquote>
      </div>
      
      <div class='hentry member_contribution'>
        <a name='S6CV0424P2_20040916_CWS2_476'>  </a>
        <blockquote cite='http://hansard.millbanksystems.com/people/ms-maria-eagle' class='contribution_text entry-content'>
          <a class='speech-permalink permalink' href='#S6CV0424P2_20040916_CWS2_476' title='Link to this speech by Ms Maria Eagle' rel='bookmark'>&sect;</a>
          <cite class='member author entry-title'><a href="/people/ms-maria-eagle" title="Ms Maria Eagle">Maria Eagle</a></cite>
          <p class="first-para">DWP was formed in June 2001 from the former Department of Social Security (DSS), and parts of the former Department for Education and Employment (DfEE) including the Employment Service. The first year for which figures for the cost of running the former DSS canteen facilities are available is the financial year 1998&#x2013;99 for which the cost was &#x00A3;2.7 million. The most recent figures available for DWP are for the financial year 2003&#x2013;04 for which the cost was &#x00A3;3.7 million. Information is not available centrally for the former DfEE.</p>
        </blockquote>
      </div>
